    Class Description
    Ball
    Represents the Movable Ball for the game.
    Blockage
    A Blockage is a rectangular shape that blocks the motion of a ball.
    Body
    A Body is the default class for an object that is representing a Planet.
    CalcHelp
    Class that provides several frequently used methods across classes
    CircularShape
    Abstraction for any object that is to be drawn in a circular way.
    GoalPost
    CircularShape representing the goal circle in Levels.
    Level
    A Level is the generic structure for each level's storage information.
    Moon
    Represents a orbiting Body.
    MovableCircularShape
    Abstraction for Circular Shapes that are movable.
    Point2d
    Mathematical structure for representing Cartesian points with double precision.
    Star
    A Star is a visual component that is simply a colored circle that is drawn in the background.
    Vector2d
    Representation of a two dimensional mathematical vector.
    WarpPoint
    A WarpPoint is a structure that allows the ball to be teleported to the next warpPoint available.
